mahakavi kalidasu ( telugu : &lt;unk&gt; &lt;unk&gt; , english : mahakavi ) is a 1960 telugu biographical film based on the life of kalidas poet kalidas kalidas in the lead roles and music composed by pendyala nageswara rao . starring akkineni nageswara rao , anjali devi in the lead roles and music composed by pendyala nageswara rao .